Devotee： What does Maharshi think of the theory of universal illusion
(Mâyâ)!

Maharshi： What is Mâyâ! It is only Reality.

D： Is not Mâyâ illusion?

M： Mâyâ is used to signify the manifestations of the Reality. Thus Mâvâ
is only Reality.
